Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph chapter status

chapter status

Purpose:
  Print one chapter's current stage and stored artifacts.

Usage:
  wikigraph chapter status <path> --chapter <id> [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]

Output shape:
  Chapter: <id>
  Title: <title-or-[untitled]>
  Stage: <planned|source|reading-graph|reading-summary>
  Source Units: <count>
  Children: <count>
  Graph: yes|no
  Summary: yes|no

Behavior:
  - Does not call an LLM provider.
  - Does not mutate the archive.
  - `Source Units` is the number of stored source records for that chapter.
  - `Graph` reports whether chapter Reading Graph data is present.
  - `Summary` reports whether the final chapter summary is present.

See also:
  - wikigraph chapter list --help
  - wikigraph queue --help
  - wikigraph help command
